					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Usually, you'd make a lookup table from metatile numbers to the tile numbers for the top left, top right, bottom left, and bottom right tiles of the metatile. Then you'd either have a fifth table for the attribute value or do like SMB1 and use the upper 2 bits of the metatile number for the attribute.</div>

